= TTF_SetFontStyle =

Set the font style.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void TTF_SetFontStyle(TTF_Font *font, int style);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handlea
|-
|'''style'''
|style flags OR'ed
|}

== Remarks ==

Setting the style clears already generated glyphs, if any, from the cache.

